any operates  neiman marcus stores across the united states and two bergdorf goodman stores in manhattan neiman marcus largest market is the south florida msa where they operate five stores the company also operates  last call clearance centers and two horchow finale furniture outlets these store operations total more than five million square feet  m² gross neiman marcus direct conducts both print catalog and online operations under the neiman marcus horchow and bergdorf goodman brand names under the neiman marcus brand neiman marcus direct primarily offers womens apparel accessories and home furnishings horchow offers upscale home furnishings linens decorative accessories and tabletop items they have also launched a new blog outlining the latest news in the fashion world and beyond until recently the neiman marcus group owned majority interest in kate spade llc a manufacturer of handbags and accessories in october  the company purchased all minority interest for approximately  million and in november  sold  ownership to liz claiborne inc for approximately  million another recent divestiture was a majority interest in gurwitch products llc which manufactures laura mercier cosmetics to alticor inc for approximately  million the christmas bookedit his and hers and fantasy giftsedit in  customers could buy a  kitchen computer to help with recipes since  neiman marcus has issued an annual christmas catalog which gets much free publicity from the national media for a tradition of unusual and extravagant gifts not sold in its stores some have included the his and hers themed items trips and cars see below in  stanley marcus introduced a new tradition of having extravagant and unusual gifts in each years christmas catalog the christmas book the idea was sparked when journalist edward r murrow contacted marcus to ask if the store would be offering anything unusual that might interest his radio listeners marcus invented on the spot an offering of a live black angus bull accompanied by a sterling silver barbecue cart subsequently altering the catalog to include his new idea priced at  at one point the neiman marcus christmas catalog carried the distinction of being the item most stolen from recipients mailboxes prompting a chicago postmaster to suggest the company switch to enclosing the catalogs in plain brown wrappers neimans fantasy gifts in the christmas book have included a  million submarine mummy cases that contained an actual mummy seats from ebbets field and a  million cobalt valkyriex plane the most expensive item was a boeing business jet for over  million other christmas giftsedit in  neimanmarcus in dallas was one of two stores in the nation — the other being wanamakers in philadelphia — to offer computerbased assistance in selecting christmas gifts the process worked by comparing information on the recipient to a computerized list of the  items available at neimanmarcus then providing a printout of the  best suggestions one person testing the computer filled out the questionnaire as if he were president john f kennedy shopping for gifts in excess of  for his wife the computer suggested a yacht during the apollo  mission in december  marilyn lovell wife of astronaut jim lovell who was the command module pilot received as a christmas present a mink coat that was delivered to her by a neiman marcus driver in a rollsroyce car the coat was wrapped in royal blue wrapping paper with two styrofoam balls — one for the earth and the other for the moon — and had a card that read to marilyn from the man in the moon in  neiman marcus partnered up with target corporation to create a holiday collection featuring  designers from the council of fashion designers of america cfda the piece collection featured apparel accessories and even some gifts for dogs controversyedit in  neiman marcus settled a federal claim for falsely claiming that some of their products contained fake fur when tests by the humane society of the united states showed it was actually real fur from raccoon dogs neiman marcus did not admit guilt but promised to adhere to federal fur labeling laws the fur act for the next twenty years referencesedit  httpphxcorporateirnetphoenixzhtmlcpirolgovmanage  neiman marcus group  company contacts corporateirnet   neiman abraham lincoln from the handbook of texas online  a b william schack neimanmarcus of texas article commentary   september   a b c d e f history of the neiman marcus group inc – fundinguniverse fundinguniversecom retrieved december     a b historical timeline from neiman marcus online  stanley marcus timeline texas monthly march   schack p   fashions mr stanley knows best time september     frank x tolbert neimanmarcus texas new york henry holt and company  page   tolbert  page   neiman marcus fortnight  news and communications  smu smuedu october   retrieved december     neiman marcus in pact for new cleveland store neiman marcus group inc highbeamcom   stanley marcus advertising hall of fame advertisinghalloffameorg september   retrieved december     neiman marcus in b buyout cnn money may    moin david august   neiman marcus inches closer to ipo wwd retrieved august     moin david september   neiman marcus profits rise wwd retrieved september     moin david october   neimans deal nearly done wwd retrieved october     halkias maria august   neiman marcus files for initial public offering of stock the dallas morning news retrieved august     nam diamond selling for n million africa allafricacom    form q from neiman marcus website march    rick ratliff knight news service the ultimate present  texas firms take pride in unusual gift offerings the lima news lima ohio november    mouse ranch — perfect christmas gift upi story the news port arthur texas october   — gives  as date of introduction  tom johnson junk for xmas at  the gettysburg times gettysburg pennsylvania december    murray raphel an interview with stanley marcus direct marketing vol  no  october  pp   wahba phil o